      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a mechanically sound example of the E46 platform, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS. Power is delivered via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. The suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein dampers to sharpen turn-in, while the braking system retains its factory-spec heat dissipation capabilities. A driver-focused machine with a robust powertrain and excellent throttle response.",
